name: Project template B (less)
description:
A project template to organize your design work and Figma pages.


Ever felt the pain of trying to navigate and find what you're looking for in someone else's design files?


This file template contains a starting point to organize your Figma files, in an attempt to reduce this pain point. Add any pages and sections as you need to organize a design file within your team.


To get started, duplicate this Figma file, then change the duplicated file to suit your needs.
